本关系图谱基于 [D3.js](https://d3js.org/) 进行绘制。一个简单的可交互示例展示在 [Observable](https://observablehq.com/@uuanqin/demo-relation-graph) 中。

<div id="main-graph" style="width: 100%; height: 600px;"></div>

如果你也想构建类 Obsidian 的博客，详见 [[hexo-filter-titlebased-link：构建你的数字花园|这篇文章]]。

<style>
/* 默认浅色模式 */
#main-graph {
  background-color: #f8f9fa;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid #eef0f2;
  box-shadow: inset 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: all 0.3s ease; /* 包含背景色的平滑过渡 */
}

/* 深色模式适配 */
/* 注意：根据你主题的具体实现，[data-theme='dark'] 可能需要换成 .dark-mode */
[data-theme='dark'] #main-graph {
  background-color: #1d1e22;    /* 深色背景 */
  border-color: #2c2d32;        /* 深色边框 */
  box-shadow: inset 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); /* 调整内阴影感 */
}

/* 悬停效果 */
#main-graph:hover {
  box-shadow: inset 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05), 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
}

[data-theme='dark'] #main-graph:hover {
  box-shadow: inset 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), 0 5px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}
</style>
<script src="/js/public/force-graph.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/public/d3.v7.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/relation_graph.js"></script>
<script>
  (function() {
    const run = () => {
      if (typeof initKnowledgeGraph === 'function') {
        initKnowledgeGraph('main-graph', '/api/backlinks.json', false);
      } else {
        // 如果脚本还没加载完，等 100ms 再试
        setTimeout(run, 100);
      }
    };
    run();
  })();
</script>
